{"id":"api/core/NgZoneOptions","title":"NgZoneOptions","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/NgZoneOptions\", \"name\": \"NgZoneOptions\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L436-L502\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L436-L502\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngzoneoptions\">NgZoneOptions<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#ngzoneoptions\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label interface\">interface</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">用於配置事件並使用 <code><a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideZoneChangeDetection</a></code> 執行合併。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Used to configure event and run coalescing with <code><a href=\"api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\" class=\"code-anchor\">provideZoneChangeDetection</a></code>.</p>\n\n\n  </section><section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"interface-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZoneOptions</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#eventCoalescing\"><span class=\"member-name\">eventCoalescing</span>?: boolean</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#runCoalescing\"><span class=\"member-name\">runCoalescing</span>?: boolean</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n\n\n</section>\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n    <li><p>provideZoneChangeDetection</p></li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n  \n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"instance-properties\">屬性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NgZoneOptions#instance-properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>屬性</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"eventCoalescing\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">eventCoalescing</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">（可選）指定或不指定合併事件變更檢測。考慮以下情況。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Optionally specify coalescing event change detections or not.\nConsider the following case.</p>\n</div>\n          <code-example>\n&lt;div (click)=\"doSomething()\"&gt;\n  &lt;button (click)=\"doSomethingElse()\"&gt;&lt;/button&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">單擊按鈕時，由於事件冒泡，將呼叫兩個事件處理程式，並觸發 2 次變更檢測。我們可以合併此類事件以僅觸發變更檢測一次。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">When button is clicked, because of the event bubbling, both\nevent handlers will be called and 2 change detections will be\ntriggered. We can coalesce such kind of events to only trigger\nchange detection only once.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">預設情況下，此選項將是 false。因此，事件將不會被合併，並且變更檢測將被觸發多次。如果此選項設定為 true，則變更檢測將透過排程動畫幀來非同步觸發。因此在上面的情況下，變更檢測將只會觸發一次。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">By default, this option will be false. So the events will not be\ncoalesced and the change detection will be triggered multiple times.\nAnd if this option be set to true, the change detection will be\ntriggered async by scheduling a animation frame. So in the case above,\nthe change detection will only be triggered once.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"runCoalescing\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">runCoalescing</span>?: boolean</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">（可選）指定 <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a>#run()</code> 方法呼叫是否應合併為單個變更檢測。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Optionally specify if <code><a href=\"api/core/NgZone\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgZone</a>#run()</code> method invocations should be coalesced\ninto a single change detection.</p>\n</div>\n          <p translation-result=\"on\">考慮以下情況。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Consider the following case.</p>\n\n<code-example>\nfor (let i = 0; i &lt; 10; i ++) {\n  ngZone.run(() =&gt; {\n    // do something\n  });\n}\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">這種情況會多次觸發變更檢測。使用 ngZoneRunCoalescing 選項，事件迴圈中的所有變更檢測只會觸發一次。此外，變更檢測是在 requestAnimation 中執行的。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">This case triggers the change detection multiple times.\nWith ngZoneRunCoalescing options, all change detections in an event loop trigger only once.\nIn addition, the change detection executes in requestAnimation.</p>\n\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n  \n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgZone\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#eventCoalescing\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#instance-properties\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#ngzoneoptions\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#runCoalescing\n - api/core/NgZoneOptions#see-also\n - api/core/provideZoneChangeDetection\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/cn/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L436-L502\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/16.1.0-next.3/packages/core/src/application_ref.ts#L436-L502\n-->"}